I think we're gonna need a bigger boat.

465
00:36:42,055 --> 00:36:44,474
- 大小没关系
- 真是个神话
- Size doesn't matter.
- That's a myth.

466
00:36:44,474 --> 00:36:47,352
它会进得去
那个设备会把它吸进去
It'll fit. The device traps the creature inside.

467
00:36:47,394 --> 00:36:49,771
你只要保证它进到那个安全壳里就行了
You just need to make sure, it's all
the way inside the containment vessel

468
