00:37:13,211 --> 00:37:15,088
该死的
Son of a bitch.

470
00:37:15,088 --> 00:37:16,214
怎么了？
What happened?

471
00:37:16,256 --> 00:37:18,592
那个东西看了一眼   然后走了
The damn thing took one look and went away.

472
00:37:18,633 --> 00:37:21,595
